description: Ludovic Orban said he hoped his party would still be able to put together a majority.
title: Romanian PM Ludovic Orban resigns after poor election result
title_page: Romanian PM Ludovic Orban resigns after poor election result - BBC News
maintext: Turnout was a record low of 33%. Romania is one the poorest countries in the EU and millions of its citizens have moved abroad in recent years in search of better lives - in particular to western EU member states.
